org.vngx.jsch.kex

Class DHGroupKexAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vngx.jsch.kex.KexAlgorithm
      • org.vngx.jsch.kex.AbstractDHKexAlgorithm
        • org.vngx.jsch.kex.DHGroupKexAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Algorithm
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DHGroup14KexAlgorithm, DHGroup1KexAlgorithm

    public abstract class DHGroupKexAlgorithm
extends AbstractDHKexAlgorithm

    Base implementation of KexAlgorithm for performing the two standard Diffie Hellman based key exchange as described in RFC 4253. Two REQUIRED key exchange methods have been defined: 

            diffie-hellman-group1-sha1 REQUIRED
        diffie-hellman-group14-sha1 REQUIRED

    Both methods use the same algorithm/packets, just a different Oakley group.

    RFC 4253 - The Secure Shell (SSH) Transport Layer Protocol: Diffie-Hellman Key Exchange

    Author:
    Michael Laudati
    See Also:
    DiffieHellman, KexAlgorithm
